events.name: Last 2015 Drone Fun FPV Meetup!
events.description:
RESCHEDULED DUE TO WEATHER! 


2015 has been a great year for FPV, and this will be our last meetup before 2016. Location: nr Holland Village - nice trees, good space for acro/racing/cruising - my last video from this location: One Pack N.B. Weather permitting!  This time of year is a high risk of rain in the afternoon, please check the weather forecast on the day! 


As always, the following rules apply: 1) Don't switch on your VTx without pre-announcing it to fliers currently in the air and waiting for their confirmation 2) Make sure you know your VTx frequency and are able to adjust it 3) During racing, if you're not currently racing do not switch on at all, until the current race is complete 4) Don't fly beyond your own abilities Read up on FPV etiquette! We're a friendly and encouraging group though, so even if you're a beginner we'll help you to get started. NB - This is a casual meetup and all attendees are responsible for their own safety and liability.
events.location: Holland Village FPV Space, 17 Holland Drive, Singapore

events.name: Shapeways Singapore Meetup @ Funbie Studios
events.description: As we near the holiday season, it would be a great time to get started to meet all you great Shapies in Singapore! Coinciding with the Singapore 3D Printing Meetup held in the new Funbie Studios space in Funan, we will have pieces from Shapeways in different materials on display and some cool folks who have been using it for their projects will be hanging out too, sharing their design and print experiences as well as some sample prints. We will also have some door gifts too (while stocks last)! Exact location to be announced soon and looking forward to seeing all of you there! =)
events.location: Funbie Studios, Funan DigitaLife Mall, Singapore
